description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-The bronze statue of Dr. Clark
-Otaru Canal
-The Road to Heaven in Shiretoko Shari
-Lake Mashu in Winter
-Goryōkaku (Japanese star fort)
-Shirohige Waterfall in the Winter Night
-Kaminoko ike Lake
-Shirogane Blue Pond
-Lake Onnetō & Mount Meakan
-The Dance of the Red-crowned Crane in Kushiro Marsh
name: Hokkaido - Most beautiful places in Japan -
